  ${
    $d G x y z $.  $d R x y z $.
    ringabl.1 $e |- G = ( 1st ` R ) $.
    $( A ring's addition operation is an Abelian group operation.  (Contributed
       by Steve Rodriguez, 9-Sep-2007.) $)
    ringabl $p |- ( R e. Ring -> G e. Abel ) $=
      ( vx vy vz cring wcel cabl crn cxp c2nd cfv wf wa cv co wceq w3a wral
      wrex eqid ringi pm3.26d ) AGHZBIHZBJZUGKUGALMZNZUEUFUIODPZEPZUHQZFPZUHQUJ
